<title type="html"><![CDATA[Re: Classic Explorer Skin that displays on initial/main page]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.classicshell.net/forum/viewtopic.php?t=6423&amp;p=27947#p27947"><![CDATA[
If your PC came with Windows 10, chances are that it will have USB 3.0, UEFI, GPT partitions etc and may not have a Compatibility Support Module. It might be hard or impossible to install Windows 7 on it but Windows 8.1 with Classic Shell will give you an experience highly similar to Windows 7.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.classicshell.net/forum/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=54">Gaurav</a> — Tue Aug 02, 2016 11:36 am</p><hr />
]]></content>
